node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Over the last 3 years I've made over $15M in sales with my eCommerce businesses. Here is how did it. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks In my 2nd year of college got introduced to eCommerce. saw some of my friends having success with it, so decided to try myself. was a broke college student and just wanted to make some extra money.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared oks started multiple dropshipping stores tried it all -Dropshipping cheap products -Building brands from scratch -Making viral ads heard Basically all the strategies everyone talk about, but none of it really worked for me.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ok lost every dollar in my bank account and even got into debt starting all those businesses and made no profit. But was determined to make eCommerce work and in my 3rd year of college, came across high ticket dropshipping.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jard_ realized the potential of selling expensive products( $1000+) from the US suppliers, using Google ads and without ever needing to buy buy inventory.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks decided to give eCommerce one more try. spent all my free time, even the breaks between classes, building my business. was contacting suppliers, building stores, looking for products, answering customer questions, etc.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ _oks And it paid off. 8 months later, month. was making $10K per Even before graduated from college| hit a 6-figure income with my dropshipping stores.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Over the last 3 years, I've made over $15M in online sales and built 5 eCommerce businesses. I've then used that money to invest in real estate stocks, and crypto.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_oks Throughout my journey learned that the way to succeed in eCommerce is to: -Sell high ticket products -Use U.S. suppliers -Use Google ads -Have great customer support'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jared Oks @jared_ok So this is the story of how started my journey as an entrepreneur. Folow me if you'd ike to learn more about eCommerce, I'm sharing lots of value daily about what learned from building my eCommerce businesses.'.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 20, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'RICHEST MAN EVER Mansa Musa was the king of TIMBUKTU and lived between 1280 and 1337. His net worth was around $400 billion. BUSINESS INSTANTLY'.

node.text:
Mansa Musa is regarded as the richest person to ever live...he created this wealth from mining salt, gold deposits, elephant ivory, etc.

He initially inherited a kingdom that was already wealthy, but his work with expanding trade made the kingdom the wealthiest in Africa.

He net worth as been estimated as $400B in today's money, but it's impossible to pin down a number.

Follow us @businessinstantly

Robinhood recently went public and opened at $38 a share. Rappers Nas and Snoop invested at $0.20 per share in the original Series A round. Investing early is how real wealth is built.'.

node.text:
Nas is big into investing in startup companies, or companies just starting out in the stock market. In 2014 he invested $4.5M in Ring and made $40M when Ring sold to Amazon.

This is what sets artists apart from entrepreneurs/investors. Snoop and Nas are making big money because they're diversifying big time.
